Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.46,0:01:42.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible... The Chancellor\Nis one of those monsters?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.46,0:01:44.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Orders, ma'am?\NWhat about the attack?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.01,0:01:46.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We haven't received instructions. Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.06,0:01:52.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.27,0:01:55.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?\NFire your cannon!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.39,0:01:58.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Look at that live feed!\NSomething weird is going on!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.06,0:02:01.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- What live feed?\N- Switch your drones to standby mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.53,0:02:09.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The enemy's withdrawing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.62,0:02:20.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is bad... What is the Council\Ngoing to do about this?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.46,0:02:23.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,L-Let go of His Excellency!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.09,0:02:27.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Stand down! This is not someone\Nwho deserves your oath of loyalty!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.09,0:02:28.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- It's war!\N- What about those students, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.84,0:02:30.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- It's Dorssian soldiers who are doing this!\N- Like you can believe anything Dorssia says.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.47,0:02:33.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If the Chancellor himself is one\Nof these hazardous organisms,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.35,0:02:35.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,how can anything\NDorssia does be trusted?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.89,0:02:37.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't believe it...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.10,0:02:38.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How much of what\Nhe said is true?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.90,0:02:41.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- We did it!\N- Not much fun, is it, you Dorssian bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.86,0:02:43.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This will turn the tide!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.78,0:02:45.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This also spells the end of the\NDorssia-ARUS alliance, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.94,0:02:50.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Can we... go back to school?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.20,0:02:52.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.74,0:02:54.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Though that all depends on\Nwhat stance ARUS takes after this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.74,0:02:59.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Things look bad for Dorssia.\NThey're looking at a civil war at this rate.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.04,0:03:04.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We staked it all on one roll of the dice,\Nand that turned the tables!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.13,0:03:11.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We did it!\NWe did it, Yamada!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.64,0:03:20.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.72,0:03:27.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- What the?\N- What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.50,0:03:41.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You lowly Valvrave knockoff...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.89,0:03:52.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Akira-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.05,0:03:55.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cain, Pino is in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.01,0:03:58.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Plu. I'm going to fulfill\Nmy promise to you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.57,0:04:08.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?\NThings were just getting good!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.28,0:04:13.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,According to reports we've just received,\Nthe scene we just witnessed
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.87,0:04:17.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,was doctored by Class 7\NSpecial Hazard Organisms.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.41,0:04:21.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So it was all a ploy by those students?\NOr rather, those monsters?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.25,0:04:24.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- What the hell, it was fake?!\N- See, what did I tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.25,0:04:27.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Boy, what a relief!\N- So those students are the only monsters, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.30,0:04:30.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How could this have happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.01,0:04:32.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They probably leaned on the media\Nbehind the scenes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.26,0:04:33.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This quickly?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.14,0:04:38.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This means that we can't just\Nslug it out with these people.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.43,0:04:41.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Give them doctored footage to analyze and\Nhave them lend credence to the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.81,0:04:44.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For the time being, the situation\Nappears to be quieting down.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.85,0:04:50.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Magiuses are in their shadows,\Nand all is right with the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.57,0:04:56.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Council of 101 is composed of the\Nworld's most influential people.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.10,0:05:02.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How many incidents and accidents do you think\Nwe have arranged over the centuries?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.31,0:05:21.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's powerful...\NThis is Unit 2?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.41,0:05:38.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cain! This is for H-neun!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.29,0:05:51.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now it makes sense. L-elf's infiltration\Nwas your handiwork, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.52,0:06:08.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They're fighting each other?\NDid L-elf set this up?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.23,0:06:10.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't! Stay back, Akira-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.07,0:06:10.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.90,0:06:12.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You can't do anything,\Nnot with damage like that!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.36,0:06:17.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,X-eins, don't go too far\Nahead by yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.33,0:06:25.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, you're turning traitor\Ntoo, Highness...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.58,0:06:26.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Q-vier!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.71,0:06:32.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Valvraves and now the Perfection Army...\NIt's a veritable feast today!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.30,0:06:34.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness you're\Nall right, Mr. President!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.17,0:06:38.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,At present, ARUS forces are keeping their\Ndistance from the Valvrave battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.51,0:06:41.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Assemble all staff officers\Naboard my flagship!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.26,0:06:44.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All forces are to cease hostilities\Nuntil we reach a decision!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.54,0:07:09.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It can do things that are\Nthat different from ours?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.50,0:07:17.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can still fight! This is\Nno time to be stingy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.76,0:07:24.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can still fight!\NI can fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.49,0:07:43.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This pilot is more competent\Nthan before, but still...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.79,0:07:54.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...readiness evaluation, D.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.63,0:08:03.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Stop this, Q-vier!\NCain killed H-neun!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.26,0:08:09.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So what if he did? Killing a traitor\Nis a good thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.64,0:08:12.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hear me out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.73,0:08:16.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"Death to traitors."\NThat's what we swore, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.32,0:08:20.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Though I'm just happy to get\Nthe chance to fight someone tough!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.83,0:08:27.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cain!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.58,0:08:31.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You'll pay!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.71,0:08:36.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You betrayed H-neun!\NAnd my heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.59,0:08:41.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sacrificing oneself for one's friends\Nis noble. I don't begrudge you that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.72,0:08:43.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,At point blank...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.59,0:08:46.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be worth dying\Nif I can take you with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.53,0:09:10.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,An attack you staked your life on.\NBrilliantly played, X-eins.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.20,0:09:11.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you a readiness\Nevaluation of A.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.46,0:09:18.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,H-neun,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.40,0:09:24.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,even at a time like this,\NI know you'd be cracking wise...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.77,0:09:38.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Haruto Tokishima!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.82,0:09:42.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Someone like you, who only recently began\Ncombat training, can't defeat Cain!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.90,0:09:47.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe not, but I have to try!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.66,0:09:51.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My point is, I will fight with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.47,0:09:55.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have reasons to defeat him\Nthat surpass even yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.83,0:09:57.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So use me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.63,0:09:59.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right! Body-jack you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.79,0:10:04.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Between my body, which has had combat techniques\Ndrilled into it by him, and your curse...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.34,0:10:05.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We can do it together!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.44,0:10:20.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right, let's\Nwrap this up, shall we?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.87,0:10:40.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That speed and that precise sword\Ntechnique... Is that you, L-elf?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.42,0:10:42.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're still alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.42,0:10:45.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We won't be silenced by you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.60,0:10:59.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You know, Haruto, when I heard that\Nyour memories were disappearing,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.77,0:11:01.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I was actually looking\Nforward to it a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.77,0:11:05.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, who can compete against\Na childhood friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.44,0:11:10.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you lost your memories,\NI'd be on an even footing with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.99,0:11:12.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a horrible person, aren't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.83,0:11:15.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The JIORan Module is moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.70,0:11:19.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A Valvrave!\NThere's more left!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.67,0:11:20.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Q-vier!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.79,0:11:23.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cannon fire has been forbidden!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.04,0:11:25.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget that VIPs from\Nour own country are inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.84,0:11:30.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Two Kirschbaums are en route.\NLieutenants A-drei and Q-vier!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.55,0:11:33.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A-drei... I can't offer you\Nany direct support.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.22,0:11:39.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I know that Haruto\Nwill choose Shoko,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.44,0:11:43.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but I promised myself that\NI wouldn't give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.54,0:11:56.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hostilities have been suspended!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.95,0:12:00.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll deal with you after I\Ntake out that Valvrave!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.73,0:12:22.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So that's why he'd been\Nusing a Waffe's shield...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.02,0:12:30.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's my A-drei...\NI knew you'd be tough!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.24,0:12:32.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Q-vier...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.53,0:12:38.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I knew you'd be the best...\NYou're so cool...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.93,0:13:03.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You understand nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.84,0:13:08.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Council of 101 is no evil secret society.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.71,0:13:12.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We are champions of justice who\Nsafeguard the peace of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.49,0:13:14.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're saying the Council\Nis the good guys?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.70,0:13:18.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It was humans\Nwho attacked us first!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.29,0:13:24.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We desired only coexistence, but\Nhumanity feared and attacked us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.87,0:13:29.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Legends of supernatural monsters around the\Nworld are a chronicle of Magius suffering!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.55,0:13:33.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It is for that reason that we,\Nover the course of many years,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.13,0:13:35.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,made deals with\Nthe world's leading figures.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.84,0:13:40.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We Magiuses have lived in secret so as\Nnot to arouse the fear of humanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.27,0:13:41.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And in return...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.85,0:13:46.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...they tacitly allow us to prey upon\Na certain number of humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.15,0:13:51.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It is only because of the Council system that humanity\Nhas been kept safe from fear and chaos!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.44,0:13:55.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In short, the ones who threaten\Nthe peace and order of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.57,0:13:58.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,are you people\Nand your Valvraves!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.08,0:14:00.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's your excuse?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.62,0:14:09.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Was what we did right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.38,0:14:11.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You saw it! You saw how\NHaruto Tokishima didn't die!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.96,0:14:17.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I did. But I didn't see him\Nkilling your father, Iori.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.31,0:14:23.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.31,0:14:26.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ma'am, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.98,0:14:31.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A teacher can't sit idly by\Nat time like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.69,0:14:34.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Find out? Find out how?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.82,0:14:38.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We'll talk. That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.87,0:14:44.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The thing about the truth is, you'll never know\Nwhat it is unless you come out and ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.75,0:14:55.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, big brother!\NI don't hate this human!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.26,0:14:59.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do that! He's one of the people\Nwho locked us up in these machines
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.34,0:15:01.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,to try to use us\Nas a power source!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.89,0:15:10.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No! We're leaking Runes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.16,0:15:22.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Can't we... win against him?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.87,0:15:27.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We walked hand in hand with history,\Nwere hurt, and came to a realization.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.96,0:15:32.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A system where there could be no conflict\Nbetween us meant living separately{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.50,0:15:35.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Very well, let's put\Nan end to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.59,0:15:38.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll eliminate you two\Nand reclaim our peace!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.10,0:15:43.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're coming, Pino!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.06,0:15:46.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.60,0:15:50.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.31,0:15:53.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You had considered trying to live\Ntogether with humanity, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.94,0:15:56.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But you gave up because\Nyou had been hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.78,0:16:01.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You built up a wall of lies\Nso neither would hurt the other.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.49,0:16:05.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He was my friend even after he\Nlost his guiding light,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.79,0:16:10.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,he picked himself up\Nto make her dream a reality!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.67,0:16:14.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And the girl that I love,\Neven after losing her father,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.46,0:16:18.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,even though he was the\Nprime minister, she kept on fighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.51,0:16:21.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Its power is increasing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.05,0:16:25.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For all our friends who haven't given up\Neven after being hurt again and again,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.89,0:16:27.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,we can't lose to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.35,0:16:33.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A coup?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.02,0:16:35.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now, of all times?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.98,0:16:38.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In seven locations\Nthat we know of.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.19,0:16:40.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They're breaking out simultaneously\Nall across Dorssian territory.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.57,0:16:44.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We Royalists have long awaited\Nthe right time to take action.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.02,0:16:49.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Regardless of the veracity of the information\Nbrought to us by the boy named L-elf,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.08,0:16:50.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}it provides sufficient pretext.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.16,0:16:54.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Excellency. This is a golden opportunity for\Nthe Royalists to rise up and turn the tables.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.83,0:16:56.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- What's the "Council of 101"?\N- Looks like a list of those monsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.17,0:16:58.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Check this out!\N- Hey, that's the president of the Winkers Company!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.13,0:16:59.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.26,0:17:00.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is a hoax!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.51,0:17:02.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps, but some of it is true!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.22,0:17:05.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It is not a problem.\NWe will deal with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.55,0:17:06.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,New information, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.85,0:17:08.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The president of the Global Bank\Nhas been taken into custody!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.89,0:17:11.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Preposterous! He isn't\Na member of the Council!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.90,0:17:17.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They're being whipped into a frenzy\Nby some made-up stories?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.48,0:17:20.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Targets have been apprehended.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.86,0:17:24.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Was it wise to trust\Nthat list, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.07,0:17:28.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Our only option is to take action now!\NBefore the monsters can band together!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.24,0:17:32.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If we play this right, we might be\Nable to get rid of the Magiuses.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.37,0:17:37.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We don't want a future that was given up on\Nand closed off from the very beginning!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.71,0:17:38.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.55,0:17:45.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...our friends never gave up,\Nso I can't, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.01,0:17:47.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You stupid boy who knows\Nnothing of history!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.98,0:18:01.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.89,0:18:34.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Plu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.37,0:18:51.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's all over!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.09,0:19:05.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cain! Cain!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.09,0:19:08.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Plu...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.89,0:19:59.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Haruto Tokishima!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.60,0:20:01.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We've done it!\NWe've won!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.65,0:20:09.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Haruto? Is that my name?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.40,0:20:18.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He used up all his Runes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.16,0:20:25.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand any of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.33,0:20:28.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.77,0:20:31.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.72,0:20:34.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You don't remember?\NAnything at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.93,0:20:39.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Not even our pact?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.10,0:20:43.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Our fight on the Moon?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.73,0:20:46.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.36,0:20:50.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You and I, we...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.41,0:20:59.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You know me, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.33,0:21:02.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You know who I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.06,0:21:08.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.68,0:21:13.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You are my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.24,0:21:32.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Imperial Calendar, year 0.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.49,0:21:37.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This would later be known as the year\Nthe Third Galactic Empire began,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.70,0:21:44.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but it goes without saying that we never\Ncould have imagined that at the time.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.21,0:21:47.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Afterwards, pandemonium\Nbroke out across the world.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.75,0:21:53.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Seeing monsters everywhere, people sought\Nout Magiuses all over the world,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.55,0:21:59.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and eventually, neither the Council of 101 nor\Nthe existence of Magiuses could remain hidden.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.56,0:22:02.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- They found the Magiuses!\N- They're for real this time, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.98,0:22:07.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I think it was because the world had become\Ntoo connected for secrets to be kept.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.94,0:22:16.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Shoko-chan cried her eyes out.\NFor what seemed like forever.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.37,0:22:23.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After a while, she went back\Nto being her usual self.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.54,0:22:26.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But every once in a while...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.88,0:22:36.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In any case, we found ourselves\Na place to call home.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.44,0:22:57.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Our Galactic Empire started\Nfrom such a tiny country?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.49,0:23:01.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Historical beginnings are often\Nsurprisingly humble.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.95,0:23:04.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,T-There's an emergency!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.87,0:23:09.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's an intruder in the Memorial Core!\NIt's thought to be lifeform 53s!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.81,0:23:24.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What were you expecting,\Na secret weapon?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.81,0:23:30.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,These are the statues of the heroes\Nwe call "The First Knights."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.48,0:23:36.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,People who were dear to me who died\None by one when we founded this country.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.99,0:23:39.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's try to be friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.53,0:23:43.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I won't pretend that that will\Nsuddenly solve everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.45,0:23:49.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But if we do, we'll be able to take\Nall our pain and joy and go halfsies!